---
---
<header class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-content">
    <h1 class="hero-title">Pinoy Dev <span class="gradient-text">Quotes API</span></h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A free, serverless API serving humor, logic, and "hugot" from Filipino developers — in 7 dialects.</p>
    <div class="badge-row">
      <span class="badge"><span class="dot" style="background:var(--emerald)"></span> 20 Quotes</span>
      <span class="badge"><span class="dot" style="background:var(--brand-400)"></span> 7 Dialects</span>
      <span class="badge"><span class="dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></span> REST + GraphQL</span>
      <span class="badge"><span class="dot" style="background:var(--amber)"></span> OG Images</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="#playground" class="btn btn-primary">Try it now</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/CyberSphinxxx/pinoy-dev-quotes-api" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-secondary">View on GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 0 64px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top center, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
  }
  .badge-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--brand-500);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px 0 rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.39);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--brand-600);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.23);
  }
  .btn-secondary {
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--brand-400);
    background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.05);
  }
</style>
